        <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
            <h2>Condition Episode Link Type</h2>
            <p>The type of relationship that exists between a condition and the target follow-on observation.</p>
            <p>This value set has an inline code system which defines the following codes:</p>
            <p>review | flare | end</p>
        </div>
